About Modoscio Innovation Hub

Our Mission

Modoscio is the Latin word for "Eureka!" or "Now I know!".  Our mission is to provide a network of scientists and engineers to provide solutions based on applying fundamental science to disrupt industries. We strive to make the world a better place through simplification, efficiency gains, and cutting overhead.

Our Network

Our network consists of highly skilled educators from top universities such as CMU, Berkeley, and Stanford, high-level industry professionals from Microsoft, Amazon, and Google, and investors with years of experience in their respective fields, mostly located in Silicon Valley. We connect in the US, Europe, and in Latin America. 

Our Services

We offer a wide range of services including consulting, prototyping, startup assistance, and contract research. Our goal is to help our clients bring their ideas to life and achieve their business objectives.

Contact Us

Questions?

We mostly acquire contacts through face-to-face recommendation and we are selective with regards to the challenges we engage in.  Having said that, we are open to read your message to see if we are a fit. Please be precise and do not provide proprietary information in your email.
